### FarmSync API Tests

# Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5201/api
@token = 

### 1. Register a new user
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "email": "test@farmsync.com",
  "password": "Test@123",
  "firstName": "Test",
  "lastName": "User"
}

### 2. Login as admin
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "Admin@123"
}

### 3. Login as test user
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
